snippet.title: Slender: The Haunted Metro Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
You wake up in a decaying metro and you have to find your way out. The only solution is to find and collect the eight pages which are scattered all over the place but be aware of the danger deep in the darkness...

Find more at: http://adf.ly/1Y1V1h
